data.title: Jessica Harris (Hollyoaks)
data.meta_description: Jessica Harris is a fictional character from the British Channel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks, played by Jennifer Biddall. She debuted on-screen during episodes airing in October 2005. Biddal decided to leave the serial in December 2007, Jessica last appeared on 31 December 2007, and Biddall has since admitted she doesn't want to return to the serial permanently. Jessica's notable storylines include affairs, being unlucky in love, gambling and a carbon monoxide plot.
